{"tid":2272693,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"XGU Sem 2冇得pass fail","createTime":"2020-11-05T08:13:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-07T08:03:19.000Z","uid":366470,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"784e9a37e724793156dbd606ce22252666441736","tid":2272693,"uid":366470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T08:13:45.000Z","msg":"Assessment<br />\n<br />\nIn S2, we will no longer offer students three assessment options. Those options were devised in response to the uncertain situation we all faced when getting to grips with the rapid switch to online and hybrid T&amp;L over the past 12 months. They are not appropriate as a long-term measure. In S2, <span class=\"red\">we will therefore remove the pass/fail option.</span> Students will still have the option of late drop should they experience unforeseen difficulties with their courses. The deadline for students to late drop a course will be 23:59 on 9 April 2021.<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n早知sem 1 pass fail晒啲科hea讀埋佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"706d7bb9f7ee31476f9c3a6b95c4585967304a63","tid":2272693,"uid":366141,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T08:18:57.000Z","msg":"我屌你老母下個sem econ1210<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/ass